  POST /api/tally/inbound/reports/profit-loss
  POST /api/tally/inbound/reports/cash-flow
  POST /api/tally/inbound/reports/ratio-analysis

  All master/voucher endpoints: accept { "Data": [...] } (vouchers lowercase "data"). Strip \u0004 prefix from all string fields. Process: upsert on (tenant_id, tally_id).
  AlterID unchanged → skip. Action: Delete → is_active = false. full_sync: true in payload → mark absent records inactive.

  Report endpoints: accept { "report_type": "...", "period_from": "...", "period_to": "...", "generated_at": "...", "data": {...} }. Insert new row into tally_reports (do
  not update — keep history of all report snapshots).

  Ledger categorization (run during syncLedgers): derive ledger_category from group_name / parent_group:
  - contains "Debtor" → customer → auto-create/update clients
  - contains "Creditor" or "Supplier" → vendor → auto-create/update vendors
  - contains "Bank" or "Cash-in-Hand" or "Cash" → bank
  - group under Expenses → expense
  - group under Income or "Sales" → income
  - group under Fixed Assets / Current Assets / Investments → asset
  - group under Loans / Capital / Current Liabilities / Provisions → liability
  - group = "Duties & Taxes" or contains "GST" or "TDS" or "TCS" → tax
  - else → other

  Outbound GET (exact Swagger paths — Tally reads Accobot data)

  GET /api/MastersAPI/ledger-group?companyId=
  GET /api/MastersAPI/ledger-master?companyId=
  GET /api/MastersAPI/stock-master?companyId=
  GET /api/MastersAPI/stock-group?companyId=
